data.eml:eml: Cyrtodactylus rosichonariefi sp. nov. (Squamata: Gekkonidae), a new swamp-dwelling bent-toed gecko from Bunguran Island (Great Natuna), Indonesia

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Riyanto, Awal, Grismer, L. Lee, Wood, Perry L. (2015): Cyrtodactylus rosichonariefi sp. nov. (Squamata: Gekkonidae), a new swamp-dwelling bent-toed gecko from Bunguran Island (Great Natuna), Indonesia. Zootaxa 3964 (1): 114-124, DOI: http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.3964.1.8
